x-wfm-keyword
view search bug multiple word
x-wfm-problem
The viewer's search feature will not find multiple words.  Single words work fine.
terms work fine.
x-wfm-solution
This is due to a limitation in php4 versions previous to 4.0.5.
<P>In PHP 4.0.5 and later, the viewer's search feature will highlight each individual
word typed.  In versions earlier than 4.0.5, only the whole phrase typed into the search
box is highlighted.</P>
